- Configure through command line options
- Use logging module against prints
- Search and download music from vk.com - http://musicshara.ru, http://vk.com/page-1_2369282
- YYYY-MM-DD prefix
- Generate m3u playlist
- Fix ID3 tags - http://wiki.python.org/moin/UsefulModules#ID3_Handling
- Incremental download
- Stats: total songs number, found and downloaded percentage, etc
